<plot>A house in Toronto has somehow become a subway station. At first, the train only stops when Jonathan's mother is out and she doesn't believe him, but soon she sees it too, and they go to City Hall. The bureaucrats blame them for building their house in a subway station. Then Jonathan finds a mysterious man who can help in exchange for some blackberry jam.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?073892</url></doc>
